gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caaf5dddeb855dbb5aa3eff4f7bf9a17a6d004a8","tid":2402090,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"附近的JJ醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4a5392625eae3cef61b292562e9c4e5feee1c1","tid":2402090,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2d42cd44072364f84b82576bf39e3d365c89adad","tid":2402090,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"JJ醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">Sir Jamsetjee Jejeebhoy, 1st Baronet Jejeebhoy of Bombay, CMG (15 July 1783 &ndash; 14 April 1859), also spelt Jeejeebhoy or Jeejebhoy, was a Parsi-Indian merchant and philanthropist. He made a huge fortune in cotton and the opium trade with China.</code></pre><br />\n~Wikipedia"},{"pid":"79ba3b4cc53d7ef5afd0d8910b6a6a974090112b","tid":2402090,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"印度梁祝"},{"pid":"e3255d17c4123bd155dc52704a8ffaf6c693eb9a","tid":2402090,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"恐怖情人<br />\n唔統一就要武統台灣<br />\n一定係大陸人假扮印度人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a72eb18b88fdef15f80b4ae4d953660150f40d","tid":2402090,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:35:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d05c5fc967be3f74278e37735705d381bc8ebe0e","tid":2402090,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caaf5dddeb855dbb5aa3eff4f7bf9a17a6d004a8","tid":2402090,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"附近的JJ醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0